title: FireFly v1.0.7 [PD]
description:
FireFly is a cinematic action puzzler in which you must control the firefly through an array of 50 hectic, obstacle filled levels.

Guide the firefly through a dark labyrinth of twists and turns, with 50 levels over 5 unique and mysterious worlds, you'll need to think fast to outwit enemies, avoid obstacles and more!

Make your way through the diverse and engaging world of FireFly!

Features:

-50 Levels across 5 Unique zones
-Tons of diverse and interesting enemies and obstacles
-Rich, constant gameplay value
-Further support from the devs to add new levels, obstacle, worlds, and more!

What's New:

Minor Bug Fixes
